OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Networks of breeders are offering to   
OL,6, mutilate puppies to follow a social    
OL,7, media trend, a BBC investigation has   
OL,8, found.                                 
OL,10,FCutting or "cropping" ears involves    
OL,11,Fremoving part of the ear flap for      
OL,12,Fcosmetic reasons.                      
OL,14,FOne breeder told an undercover         
OL,15,Fjournalist it created a "striking" look
OL,16,Ffor the American bully breed.          
OL,18,FThe procedure is illegal in the UK, but
OL,19,Fbreeders are offering fraudulent pet   
OL,20,Fpassports to imply it was done abroad. 
